{"tid":1631510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「投票」聽日勇武應該keep住裝修定係暫緩一日？","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:26.000Z","uid":312147,"like":31,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bf232bd6836c709773913f5686fb3c356c300762","tid":1631510,"uid":312147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Keep住裝修 食住個勢佢老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />暫緩一日 俾時間文宣做嘢 同重申堅持四色原則<br />\n<br />\n我覺得節奏好重要嘅<br />\n繼續還是暫停要睇時機<br />\n留意吓大隊跟唔跟得上進化速度"},{"pid":"9859ab26e5017e14482c51df94f7154b46d3f3bd","tid":1631510,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"aac7237a13c21478ba221bc0bfca226b7d6379b1","tid":1631510,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:18.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a9a0f1073a7dca853c60c0ac68fe5be37947a89a","tid":1631510,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:21.000Z","msg":"暫緩一陣傾下文宣方向"},{"pid":"f750c4c5ad5197cb3d1306d59201538e6ac602dd","tid":1631510,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"907b842231f54cbb4052e744d99ca83bd67c3038","tid":1631510,"uid":322124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:28.000Z","msg":"[本土文宣+國際戰線] 撤銷緊急法 !!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1631430/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631430/page/1</a><br />\n聽日開始，每晚十點，一齊 Twitter tag #anti-ERO !! <br />\nThe Emergency Regulations Ordinance (ERO) is not only about anti-mask!<br />\n緊急法違反基本法既立法行政分權。<br />\nThe Emergency Regulations Ordinance (ERO) is violating the Basic Law in Hong Kong.<br />\n緊急法擴大警權濫捕。<br />\nThe Emergency Regulations Ordinance (ERO) is opening room for higher degree of police abuse in Hong Kong.<br />\n緊急法可以打壓網絡自由。<br />\nThe Emergency Regulations Ordinance (ERO) can be used to restrict HK people&rsquo; rights to access Internet.<br />\n緊急法可以凍結港人資產。<br />\nThe Emergency Regulations Ordinance (ERO) can be used for confiscating the assets of Hong Kong people."},{"pid":"71b71926237cc435a2fcc0c4408bb0cef36504c7","tid":1631510,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:18.000Z","msg":"聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9babe1613faf20455c54f3675f0adf9b60f464a8","tid":1631510,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pPuUVXO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpPuUVXO.jpg&h=8e66724e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"552858255764862e911a4f7e2225a5b5903271c3","tid":1631510,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7號晚係關鍵！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要令黨鐵全線第二日停駛</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im